text: Carl Pettersson (born 1977) is a Swedish golfer. Carl Pettersson may also refer to: * Carl Emil Pettersson (1875–1937), Swedish sailor and inspiration for Ephraim Longstocking * Carl Axel Pettersson (1874–1962), Swedish curler ==See also== *Carl Peterson (disambiguation) *Carl Petersen (disambiguation)
